shape: sequence_diagram

User: Portal User
Portal: Management Portal
Identity: Identity & Session Service
Provider: Identity Provider
Config: Configuration Store
Audit: Audit Store

User -> Portal: Start sign-in
Portal -> Identity: Request login
Identity -> Provider: Redirect authentication request
Provider -> User: Present authentication flow
User -> Provider: Complete authentication
Provider -> Identity: Return verified identity result
Identity -> Config: Load organization membership and roles
Config -> Identity: Return authorized portal context
Identity -> Audit: Record sign-in result
Identity -> Portal: Establish portal session
Portal -> User: Show permitted organizations and projects
